In Bangladesh, the AQI is based on `5 criteria pollutants` like Particulate Matter ($\text{PM}_{10}$ and $\text{PM}_{2.5}$), $\text{NO}_2$, $\text{CO}$, $\text{SO}_2$ and Ozone ($\text{O}_3$). The AQI standard for Bangladesh is given below:

